OL,3,CKey features of new major hospital
OL,4,Crevealed in plans
OL,6,FA planning application for Jersey's
OL,7,Fnew Acute Hospital at Overdale has
OL,8,Fbeen submitted.
OL,10,FThe proposals include more than 200
OL,11,Fovernight beds, higher than the number
OL,12,Fat Jersey's General Hospital, and more
OL,13,Fmodern versions of departments such as
OL,14,FAccident and Emergency.
OL,16,FThe Government says its consultation
OL,17,Fshows public support for the concept
OL,18,Fdesigns and the project timeline.
