OL,3,CKey features of new major hospital
OL,4,Crevealed in plans
OL,6,FThe Government Budget sets aside #710
OL,7,Fmillion for the island's new
OL,8,Fhealthcare facilities, which will now
OL,9,Finclude work towards creating a St
OL,10,FSaviour Health Village and the
OL,11,FKensington Place Ambulance Station.
OL,13,FIt estimates that construction of the
OL,14,FAcute Hospital should be completed by
OL,15,F2028.
OL,17,FPlans to refurbish the existing
OL,18,FOverdale facilities were considered,
OL,19,Fnamed in the Outline Business Case
OL,20,F(OBC) for the hospital project as the
OL,21,F'Do Minimum' option.
