OL,3,CKey features of new major hospital
OL,4,Crevealed in plans
OL,6,FThe OBC concluded that this choice
OL,7,Fwould add ten years to construction,
OL,8,Fincrease costs and disrupt existing
OL,9,Fhealthcare.
OL,11,FIt also believes only renewing the
OL,12,Fexisting site rather than demolishing
OL,13,Fit and starting again would see demand
OL,14,Foutstrip capacity for acute beds by
OL,15,F2030.
OL,17,FHealth Minister Tom Binet says: "The
OL,18,Foverwhelming message from the public
OL,19,Fconsultation was simply to 'get on
OL,20,Fwith' building without further delay,
OL,21,Fand that is my intent."
